<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HealthTrack - Votre Santé Connectée</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        .blob { position: absolute; filter: blur(40px); z-index: -1; opacity: 0.4; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-gray-800 antialiased overflow-x-hidden">

    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-gray-100 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="#" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-200">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-heart-pulse"></i>
                </div>
                <span>HealthTrack</span>
            </a>

            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 font-medium text-gray-600">
                <a href="#features" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">Fonctionnalités</a>
                <a href="#community" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">Communauté</a>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                {% if app.user %}
                    <a href="{{ path('app_missions_index') }}" class="hidden md:block text-gray-600 font-medium hover:text-blue-600">Mon Espace</a>
                    <a href="{{ path('front_logout') }}" class="bg-red-50 text-red-600 hover:bg-red-100 px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full font-bold transition">Déconnexion</a>
                {% else %}
                    <a href="{{ path('front_login') }}" class="hidden md:block text-gray-600 font-medium hover:text-blue-600">Se connecter</a>
                    <a href="{{ path('front_register') }}" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full font-bold shadow-lg shadow-blue-200 transition transform hover:-translate-y-0.5">
                        Commencer
                    </a>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="blob bg-blue-400 w-96 h-96 rounded-full top-0 -left-20"></div>
        <div class="blob bg-cyan-300 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bottom-0 -right-20"></div>

        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="space-y-8 animate-fade-in-up">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 text-sm font-bold border border-blue-100">
                    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 animate-pulse"></span>
                    La Santé 3.0 est arrivée
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
                    Prenez le contrôle de <br>
                    <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500">votre santé</span> dès aujourd'hui.
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
                    Une plateforme unique pour suivre vos constantes, gérer vos médicaments, prendre rendez-vous et vous engager bénévolement.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                    <a href="{{ path('front_register') }}" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg shadow-xl shadow-blue-300 hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
                        Créer un compte gratuit
                    </a>
                    <a href="#features" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-white text-gray-700 border border-gray-200 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-play text-blue-500"></i> Voir la démo
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium pt-4">
                    <div class="flex -space-x-2">
                        <img class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-white" src="https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Ali&background=random" alt="">
                        <img class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-white" src="https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Sarra&background=random" alt="">
                        <img class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-white" src="https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Mohamed&background=random" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <p>Rejoint par +10,000 utilisateurs</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative lg:h-[600px] flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="relative w-72 h-[550px] bg-gray-900 rounded-[3rem] border-8 border-gray-900 shadow-2xl z-20 transform -rotate-6">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-32 h-6 bg-gray-900 rounded-b-xl z-30"></div>
                    <div class="w-full h-full bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576091160399-112ba8d25d1d?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=634&q=80" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90">
                        <div class="absolute top-20 left-4 right-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-500">Activité Cardiaque</span>
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-heart-pulse text-red-500"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-2xl font-bold">72 BPM</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="absolute w-72 h-[500px] bg-white rounded-[3rem] border border-gray-200 shadow-xl z-10 transform rotate-6 translate-x-16 translate-y-12 hidden md:block">
                    <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
                        <div class="h-8 w-24 bg-gray-100 rounded-full"></div>
                        <div class="space-y-2">
                            <div class="h-20 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-3 flex items-center gap-3">
                                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-200 rounded-full"></div>
                                <div class="flex-1 h-2 bg-blue-200 rounded"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="h-20 bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-3 flex items-center gap-3">
                                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-200 rounded-full"></div>
                                <div class="flex-1 h-2 bg-green-200 rounded"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-blue-600 font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm mb-2">Nos 3 Métiers</h2>
                <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4">Une seule plateforme, trois espaces complémentaires</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg">
                    Votre projet regroupe trois métiers cohérents : le suivi patient, le bénévolat/missions et les annonces & donations solidaires.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Métier 1 : Espace Patient / Santé -->
                <a href="{{ path('front_login') }}" class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 border border-gray-100 group">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-red-500 text-2xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-heart-pulse"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Espace Patient</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-500">
                        Accédez à votre espace VitalTech : profil, données de santé et tableau de bord personnalisé.
                    </p>
                </a>

                <!-- Métier 2 : Bénévolat / Missions -->
                <a href="{{ path('app_missions_index') }}" class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 border border-gray-100 group">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-blue-500 text-2xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-hand-holding-hand"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Bénévolat & Missions</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-500">
                        Découvrez les missions de bénévolat, postulez, gérez vos candidatures et vos actions solidaires.
                    </p>
                </a>

                <!-- Métier 3 : Annonces & Donations -->
                <a href="{{ path('app_donation_index') }}" class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 border border-gray-100 group">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-purple-500 text-2xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-hand-holding-heart"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Annonces & Donations</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-500">
                        Consultez les annonces de besoins, créez vos propres annonces et organisez les donations associées.
                    </p>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="community" class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900 to-blue-900 -z-10"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white opacity-5 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>

        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div class="relative">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559027615-cd4628902d4a?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Volunteers" class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border-4 border-white/20">
                <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl max-w-xs hidden md:block">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-3">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 font-bold text-xl">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-hand-holding-heart"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">Impact Social</p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Rejoignez le mouvement</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">"Grâce à HealthTrack, j'ai trouvé une mission bénévole près de chez moi."</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-white">
                <span class="bg-indigo-500/30 text-indigo-100 border border-indigo-400/30 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Engagement</span>
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mt-4 mb-6 leading-tight">Plus qu'une app, une <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-400">Communauté Solidaire</span></h2>
                <p class="text-indigo-100 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                    La santé, c'est aussi l'entraide. Notre module unique de bénévolat vous permet de participer à des missions locales ou de vous inscrire à des événements de prévention.
                </p>
                
                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-cyan-400 mt-1"></i>
                        <span>Accès à des missions de bénévolat exclusives.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-cyan-400 mt-1"></i>
                        <span>Calendrier des événements de santé publique.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-cyan-400 mt-1"></i>
                        <span>Réseau d'entraide entre patients.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <a href="{{ path('app_missions_index') }}" class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
                    Devenir Bénévole
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-white border-b border-gray-100">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center divide-x divide-gray-100">
                <div class="p-4">
                    <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-600 mb-2">15k+</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-500 font-medium">Utilisateurs Actifs</div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4">
                    <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-600 mb-2">500+</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-500 font-medium">Médecins Partenaires</div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4">
                    <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-600 mb-2">98%</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-500 font-medium">Satisfaction Patient</div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4">
                    <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-600 mb-2">24/7</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-500 font-medium">Support Disponible</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-gray-50 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">Prêt à transformer votre santé ?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-10">Rejoignez des milliers de patients qui ont choisi la simplicité et la sécurité avec HealthTrack.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
                <a href="{{ path('front_register') }}" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold shadow-xl shadow-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-700 transition transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Commencer Gratuitement
                </a>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-400">Aucune carte de crédit requise • Annulable à tout moment</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-300 py-12 border-t border-gray-800">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-heart-pulse text-blue-500"></i>
                    <span>HealthTrack</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    La plateforme leader de gestion de santé connectée. Simple, Sécurisée et Solidaire.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-800 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">
            &copy; 2026 HealthTrack Inc. Tous droits réservés.
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
